                                        Server creation- Express/node js
                                        ---------------------------------

   Commands
   --------

   1)create package.json - npm init

   2)Install Express - npm i Express

   3)To run server- node index.js/nodemon index.js where index.js is the entry point (using node server or nodemon server. node server
                                                        doesn't allow auto compilation. So we use nodemon)

   4)to install nodemon- npm i -g nodemon

   5)to run after installation of nodemon - nodemon index.js     

   6)install jsonwebtoken(for jwt token) - npm i jsonwebtoken       

   7)install mangoose - npm i mangoose   

   8) install cors -  npm i cors                                   



Steps for server creation
_________________________

1)create folder for server

2)create package.json

3)install express

4)create index.js file

5)import express in index.js file

6)create an app using express

7)set up the port number

8)resolve http request from client

9)run server

10)parse json data in index.js

11)Middleware - (req,res,next)=>{}

             11.1)Application specific middleware- for the entire application

             11.2)Router specific middleware- to particular requests only

12)JWT token - to authenticate user (to make the data secure during sending)

steps to use JWT token(server creates the JWT token):
____________________________________________________

              12.1)token generation - using sign()

              12.2)validate token - using verify()

  13)db connection

            13.1)install mongoose         

            13.2)import mongoose   

            13.3)define connection string

            13.4)create model
            
            13.5)export model

    14) Promise- to deal asynchronous events

          14.1) then() -resolved state

          14.2) catch() - reject state     


     15) cors - cross origin resource sharing => (integrating front end and back end)

            15.1) install cors

            15.2)import index.js

            15.3) use cors to specify the origin in server app